      "ja": "これは何？これは本です。",
      "time": "00:00:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What's that?",
      "zh": "那是什麼？",
      "ja": "あれは何？",
      "time": "00:00:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's a box.",
      "zh": "那是一個盒子。",
